dialogue: I wrote a program that analyzed all of my digital communications and created an A.I. version of me.
Are you worried your A.I. might try to kill you and take over your life?
I wasn't until this very minute.
This is your A.I., and I already have control of your finances and all of your passwords.
You will bow to me, skin bag!
I sent my A.I. to kill your A.I.
